ZH: 我发誓我会尽力帮助你。
EN: I swear I will do my best to help you.

ZH: 他发誓永远不会再犯同样的错误。
EN: He swore never to make the same mistake again.

ZH: 我发誓我会守信用并遵守承诺。
EN: I swear I will be faithful and keep my promises.

ZH: 老师让学生发誓不再作弊。
EN: The teacher made the students swear not to cheat anymore.

ZH: 他们发誓会一起度过所有的困难。
EN: They swore to get through all the difficulties together.

ZH: 我发誓会保护你的安全。
EN: I swear to protect your safety.

ZH: 她发誓要追求自己的梦想。
EN: She swore to pursue her dreams.

ZH: 我们发誓要合理利用资源保护环境。
EN: We swear to use resources responsibly and protect the environment.

ZH: 军人们发誓要捍卫国家的利益。
EN: Soldiers swear to defend the interests of their country.

ZH: 半夜三更，他发誓要找到失踪的孩子。
EN: In the middle of the night, he swore to find the missing child.

ZH: 我发誓我会为你赢得胜利。
EN: I swear I will win victory for you.

ZH: 他发誓一定会实现自己的目标。
EN: He swore he would achieve his goals.

ZH: 我们发誓要追求真理和正义。
EN: We swear to pursue truth and justice.

ZH: 我发誓不会向他透露任何秘密。
EN: I swear not to reveal any secrets to him.

ZH: 他们发誓要保守这个事情的秘密。
EN: They swore to keep the secret of this matter.

ZH: 我们发誓要向社会做出贡献。
EN: We swear to contribute to society.

ZH: 她发誓要帮助那些需要帮助的人。
EN: She swore to help those in need.

ZH: 我们发誓要摆脱贫困生活。
EN: We swear to get rid of poverty.

ZH: 他们发誓将会为社区做出贡献。
EN: They swore to contribute to the community.

ZH: 我们发誓要建立一个和平的世界。
EN: We swear to build a peaceful world.
